highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Australia. “Tears” is the highest at #4.
“Mr. Brightside” by The Killers has been on Top Songs Australia the longest, at 2082 days straight.
“Loser” by Tame Impala is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Australia, up 61 spots at #87.
“A COLD PLAY” by The Kid LAROI is the highest new entry on Top Songs Australia at #68.
